---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import MinecraftStyleFigure from '../components/MinecraftStyleFigure.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — oomkill.dev" description="Aryan Narayan — Platform Engineer. About oomkill.dev and what this site is.">
	<div class="space-y-8 prose">
		<h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-foreground tracking-tight">About</h1>
		<MinecraftStyleFigure />
		<p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
			I'm <strong class="text-foreground">Aryan Narayan</strong>. I work as a Platform Engineer at Amagi Media Labs and love exploring how systems really work — the kind of “why does it behave like that?” that keeps me digging.
		</p>
		<p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
			I'm based in Bengaluru, India. This site is where I write about what I'm learning: systems, tooling, and ideas that stick.
		</p>
		<p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
			The name <strong class="text-foreground">oomkill</strong> is a nod to the kernel's out-of-memory killer: when things get tight, something has to give. Here, it's just words and code.
		</p>
	</div>
</Layout>
